  <steps>
    <step num="0">Heat oil in a pan over medium heat until it begins to shimmer. </step>
    <step num="1">Add the broccoli and sprinkle with salt, stirring to coat in the oil. </step>
    <step num="2">Cook for 5 minutes, without moving the broccoli. </step>
    <step num="3">Add chicken stock and place a lid on the pan, and cook for 1 minute. </step>
    <step num="4">Remove the lid and add the garlic and red pepper flakes. Stir, cooking for 1 minute. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
